The cops in Rakgoadi outside Groblersdal have launched a
massive manhunt for a group of armed suspects who were involved in a foiled
cash-in-transit robbery which occurred near Letebejane village.Limpopo cops spokesperson Colonel Moatshe Ngoepe said It is
alleged that at about 08:30 on Thursday, a cash-in-transit vehicle was
travelling along the Leeuwfontein and Apel-cross road when the driver noticed a
white Mercedes Benz and Navy blue Volvo following them.He said the occupants ultimately started shooting at them
